  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Compilation of two racing and four sports/dexterity games with these game modes.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SLOT RACE</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience slot racing like never before and enjoy the constantly changing perspectives on ten racetracks.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PURSUIT RACE</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overtake the other cars, detach all elements of the orbtrain and reach the pole position.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GUIDED BALL</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Position the ball so that you can hit it well with your desired technique. Be surprised at how far you can throw a ball and show off your skills by guiding it into the target with your eyes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CLIMBING MANIA</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb dizzying heights and collect the orbs after you've cleared the targets. Enjoy the sweeping views of the playing field.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SCRAMBLE ACTION</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sharpen your senses, focus on the targets around you and get them.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>POWER PUNCH</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel superhuman strength as you smash the massive orbs to pieces with your hands.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch the video to get an idea of how to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game instructions are shown at the beginning of each game mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimised for Meta Rift or Quest 2 via Airlink.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Does it run on your system? Have a look at the demo.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Compilation of two racing and four sports/dexterity games with these game modes.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SLOT RACE</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience slot racing like never before and enjoy the constantly changing perspectives on ten racetracks.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PURSUIT RACE</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Overtake the other cars, detach all elements of the orbtrain and reach the pole position.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GUIDED BALL</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Position the ball so that you can hit it well with your desired technique. Be surprised at how far you can throw a ball and show off your skills by guiding it into the target with your eyes.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CLIMBING MANIA</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb dizzying heights and collect the orbs after you've cleared the targets. Enjoy the sweeping views of the playing field.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SCRAMBLE ACTION</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sharpen your senses, focus on the targets around you and get them.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>POWER PUNCH</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Feel superhuman strength as you smash the massive orbs to pieces with your hands.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch the video to get an idea of how to play.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Game instructions are shown at the beginning of each game mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optimised for Meta Rift or Quest 2 via Airlink.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Does it run on your system? Have a look at the demo.</p>",
